metadata.name: Mutant Vehicles #01 – Monaco
metadata.description:
This collection is based on the award winning fine art book "Mutant Vehicles - Art on Wheels at Burning Man". 

If you buy a Mutant Vehicles NFT´ you'll receive a signed edition of the book. Hop in and settle down for a surreal ride across the Black Rock Desert.

If you buy a Alexandra Lier NFT, you do not receive commercial rights in the corresponding artwork. 

©alexandra lier
